prompts.frontCover: A minimalist, humorous birthday card illustration in a flat 2D style. In the center, a charming cartoon-style boba tea cup is anthropomorphized, wearing oversized sunglasses and lounging on a tiny beach towel. The boba cup has a cheerful, smiling expression. Next to it, a single cartoon coconut with a small paper umbrella sits in the sand. The scene is set on a stylized, minimalist beach with a simple wave line representing the ocean and a soft, pastel-colored sand area. The overall color palette is clean and bright with pastel tones. Floating above the scene in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao! Hope your day is as sweet as you are." The background is a solid, soft off-white, emphasizing the clean and elegant shapes of the illustration.
